snippet.title: Grizzly's || UPDATED || Teaser Trailer
snippet.description: This is the teaser trailer for an upcoming update to the original version of the game. The gameplay, story, and many aspects of the original game will be fleshed out to be a decent and enjoyable playing experience. It must take guts to play the same game twice!
